data.description: Fall in love from the curb. Lovely brick home located on a quiet street with NO Backyard Neighbors. 2 story entry, crown molding, wood & tile flooring, open concept floor plan, great for families or entertaining. Island kitchen is open to family room w/ great counter space & tons of cabinets, & stainless appliances. Family room w/ cozy fireplace & tons of natural light. Primary suite & en-suite bath w/ dual sinks, separate walk-in shower & soaking tub + walk-in closet. Upstairs game room. Spacious guest bedrooms w/ great closet space. Backyard w/ covered patio, storage shed & plenty of room for the family. Attached 2 car garage. Great location w/ proximity to I45 & Hwy 99, quick drive to The Woodlands, Bush Airport and downtown.
